snippet: The Underwood New Music Readings match aspiring composers with the American Composers Orchestra.
abstract: Vivien Schweitzer reviews concert of six classical music pieces by aspiring composers performed by the American Composers Orchestra at the DiMenna Center as part of its annual Underwood New Music Readings series.
lead_paragraph: The Underwood New Music Readings match aspiring composers with the American Composers Orchestra.

headline.main: Up-and-Coming Composers Secure a Valuable Friend
